Hmm. If I understand your proposal correctly, this is already in the draft, it's just that the elements have different names (for compatibility with existing UAs and authoring practices). It would look like this:<dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>&lt;html&gt; <br /> &lt;head&gt; <br />  &lt;link rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot; href=&quot;/style.css&quot; type=&quot;text/css&quot; media=&quot;screen&quot;&gt;<br />  &lt;script src=&quot;/script.js&quot; type=&quot;text/javascript&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt; <br />  &lt;link href=&quot;http://www.somesite.com/&quot; rel=&quot;author&quot; title=&quot;designer&quot;&gt; <br />  &lt;link href=&quot;http://www.someothersite.com/&quot; type=&quot;author&quot; title=&quot;programmer&quot;&gt; <br /> &lt;/head&gt; <br /> &lt;body&gt; <br />  &lt;header&gt; <br /><br />  &lt;/header&gt; <br />  &lt;nav&gt; <br /><br />  &lt;/nav&gt; <br />  &lt;article&gt; <br /><br />  &lt;/article&gt; <br />  &lt;footer&gt; <br /><br />  &lt;/footer&gt; <br /> &lt;/body&gt; <br />&lt;/html&gt;</code></dd></dl><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forums.whatwg.org/bb3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=4">zcorpan</a> — Wed May 16, 2007 11:24 pm</p><hr />
